## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

###
## ─── Dungeon Status ───
###

### Check dungeon status
GET {{host}}/dungeons/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Enter Dungeon ───
###

### Enter a visible landmark dungeon
POST {{host}}/dungeons/enter
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "poiId": "shadowfang-caverns"
}

### Enter a ruins dungeon
POST {{host}}/dungeons/enter
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "poiId": "sunken-citadel"
}

### Enter a mine dungeon
POST {{host}}/dungeons/enter
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "poiId": "ironveil-mines"
}

###
## ─── Advance Through Rooms ───
###

### Advance to the next room
POST {{host}}/dungeons/advance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Advance again (repeat as needed)
POST {{host}}/dungeons/advance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Leave Dungeon ───
###

### Leave dungeon (progress saved)
POST {{host}}/dungeons/leave
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Combat in Dungeon ───
###

### Attack dungeon monster (must be in dungeon combat)
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "attack"
}

### Cast spell in dungeon combat
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "cast",
  "spellId": "fireball"
}

### Use health potion in dungeon combat
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "use_item",
  "itemId": "health-potion"
}

###
## ─── Error Cases ───
###

### Enter dungeon when not at POI location — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/dungeons/enter
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "poiId": "the-gullet"
}

### Enter a non-dungeon POI — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/dungeons/enter
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "poiId": "thornhaven"
}

### Advance when not in dungeon — should fail (409)
POST {{host}}/dungeons/advance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Leave when not in dungeon — should fail (409)
POST {{host}}/dungeons/leave
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Try to travel while in dungeon — should fail (409)
POST {{host}}/travel/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "destinationX": 50,
  "destinationY": 50
}

### Try to rest while in dungeon — should fail (409)
POST {{host}}/rest/camp
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

### Try to shop while in dungeon — should fail (409)
GET {{host}}/shops/thornhaven
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Workflow: Full Dungeon Run ───
###

### 1. Travel to dungeon location first
POST {{host}}/travel/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "destinationX": 78,
  "destinationY": 36
}

### 2. Check travel status (wait for arrival)
GET {{host}}/travel/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Enter the dungeon
POST {{host}}/dungeons/enter
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "poiId": "shadowfang-caverns"
}

### 4. Check dungeon status
GET {{host}}/dungeons/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Advance through rooms (repeat)
POST {{host}}/dungeons/advance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Fight monsters with combat actions
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "attack"
}

### 7. Check combat status
GET {{host}}/combat/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
